learning_outcomes.en:
Upon successful completion of this course, students should:
*	have enhanced their ability to plan their work, to stick to time frames and to work both independently and in teams;
*	have improved their oral and written communication skills;
*	have developed their ability to give constructive feedback, to work with feedback on their work and to reflect on their abilities and needs;
*	have broadened their horizons through familiarizing themselves with their colleagues' work.
